quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,"Garaacdada (qalbiyada waa Qiyaamada)."
  101,2,"Maxay tahay Garaacdadu?."
  101,3,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyeyna waxay tahay Garaacdadu?"
  101,4,"Waa Maalintay dadku noqon sida baalallay kala firdhay."
  101,5,"Oo buurahu noqon sida cudbi la dhilay."
  101,6,"Qofka miisaankiisa (camallada wanaagsan) uu culeys yahay."
  101,7,"Wuxuu ku noolaan nolol barwaaqo iyo farxad leh oo raalli lagu yahay (Janno)."
  101,8,"Qofkase uu miisaankiisa (camallada wanaagsan) fudeyd yahay."
  101,9,"Hoygiisu waa Haawiya."
  101,10,"Maxaa ku ogeysiiyeyna waxay tahay?"
  101,11,"(Waa) Naar hureysa oo kuleyl badan."
